fields.physical_description:
1. box lid; card covered with blue paper; on the top is a label printed in colours to show the title; trademark and 6 named illustrations of vehicles together with UN JEU DONT ON NE SE LASSE JAMAIS and the number
1 printed in red on a yellow circle. Inside the lid is glued a printed sheet showing two structures and the list of pieces needed. 
2. box base; card covered with blue paper. 
3. instructions booklet; printed paper showing the named parts and illustrations of various constructions which can be made together with a list of the pieces required to make each. PIECES EMPLOYEES DANS LES CONSTRUCTIONS DE 'L'INVENTEUR' wooden pieces are stained yellow; blue; green or red with some of the dowel sticks of plain wood 
4. GRANDE PLAQUE A; yellow with one surface cut with four lines; the long edges drilled with one hole each and the short edges with two holes each. 5.5 x 4.3 x 1.0cm 
5. BARILLET B; tube shaped; blue with 4 lines cut into the sides and a hole drilled into each end but not through the century. 3cm x 2.5cm 
6. PLAQUE CENTRALE C; yellow with one surface cut with five lines; the long edges drilled with one hole each and the short edges with two holes each. The underside is missing a pieces at one end. 5.5 x 4.3 x 1.0cm 
7. GRAND DOME D; blue with one surface cut with four lines; one short edge has two holes drilled into it. 5.5 x 4.3 x 1.2cm 
8. PETIT DOME E; blue with two lines cut into one surface; one long edge is drilled with three holes and the other with two holes. One end of the block is missing. 4 x 3.2 1.2cm 
9. PETITE PLAQUE F; yellow with two lines cut into one surface; two holes are drilled into each long side and one into each short edge 4.5 x 3.2 x 1.0cm 
10-13. ROUE G; blue with a hole drilled through the centre of each diam. 3cm 
14. ROUE A AUBE H; blue with a hole through the centre and 6 angled cuts cuts around the outer edge. diam 3cm 
15. BOULE I; red with one line cut into the flat side. 1.5 x diam 1.5 
16-20. CLOU J; yellow peg shapes. L. 1.8cm 
21-24. PLAQUETTE CARREE K; red. 3.5 x 3cm. (24 is broken) 
25,26. PLAQUETTES RECTANGULAIRES L; red. 3 x 2cm 
27,28. PLAQUETTES RECTANGULAIRES M; green. 3 x 1.5cm 
29. ENTRETOISE N; green. 3 x 0.5cm 
30-36. CHEVILLE R; plain dowel; L. 5cm 
37-39. TRINGLE S; plain dowel; L. 10in metal junctions which are not listed as part of the equipment so may be additions from another set. They are designed to take dowel sticks to link them together to form a structure. 
40-42. singles; L. 2cm 
43. right angled junction. 
44-47. T-bar shape of three junctions 
48-50. angled shaped with three junctions 
51. box compartment divided into two parts 
52. box compartment
